<div id="course-content">    <div class="row gutter"><!-- row -->        <div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12">            <h1 class="page-title">Rich Media Communication using Adobe® Flash®</h1><!-- category title -->        </div>    </div>    <hr/>    <div class = "panel panel-default">        <div class = "panel-heading">            <h4 class = "panel-title">                <a href = "#collapseOne" data-parent = "#accordion" data-toggle = "collapse" class = "accordion-toggle">                    Flash content reaches over 98% of Internet viewers                </a>            </h4>        </div>        <div class = "panel-collapse collapse" id = "collapseOne">            <div class = "panel-body">                <p>Adobe® Flash Player is the world’s most                    pervasive software platform, used by over 2                    million professionals and reaching over 98% of                    Internet-enabled desktops in mature markets                    as well as a wide range of devices.                    <br /><br />Source: Millward Brown survey, conducted                    December 2007.                </p>            </div>        </div>    </div>    <div class = "panel panel-default">        <div class = "panel-heading">            <h4 class = "panel-title">                <a href = "#collapseTwo" data-parent = "#accordion" data-toggle = "collapse" class = "accordion-toggle">                    Growing Nature of Digital  Communications                </a>            </h4>        </div>        <div class = "panel-collapse collapse" id = "collapseTwo">            <div class = "panel-body">                <p>                    The growing popularity of the Adobe                    platform and type of digital media they                    create is changing the way we connect to the                    world witnessed by younger and younger                    people creating in programs such as Flash                    and Dreamweaver for more effective and                    immediate communications.                    <br /><br />Source: http://news.netcraft.com/archives/                    web_server_survey.html.                </p>             </div>        </div>    </div>    <div class = "panel panel-default">        <div class = "panel-heading">            <h4 class = "panel-title">                <a href = "#collapseThree" data-parent = "#accordion" data-toggle = "collapse" class = "accordion-toggle">                    OFFER YOUR STUDENTS RESUME-BUILDING CERTIFICATION                </a>            </h4>        </div>        <div class = "panel-collapse collapse" id = "collapseThree">            <div class = "panel-body">                <p>                <p>                                        Without practical work experience, landing a job right out of school can be difficult—                    especially in the competitive world of digital media. But capable students can prove                    their marketable knowledge and skills, and command a competitive advantage, through                    Adobe® Certified Associate certification. Now students can easily be tested and certified                    in this high demand area by taking the Rich Media Communication using Adobe®                    Flash Exam.                </p>                </p>             </div>        </div>    </div>    <div class = "panel panel-default">        <div class = "panel-heading">            <h4 class = "panel-title">                <a href = "#collapseFour" data-parent = "#accordion" data-toggle = "collapse" class = "accordion-toggle">                    VALIDATE VALUABLE KNOWLEDGE AND SKILLS IN ADOBE® FLASH®                </a>            </h4>        </div>        <div class = "panel-collapse collapse" id = "collapseFour">            <div class = "panel-body">                <p>                    Adobe® Flash® software is the industry standard for creating and delivering effective rich                    interactive content across desktops and devices. With Adobe® Flash,® users can integrate                    animation, video, text, audio and graphics into engaging experiences that span a wide                    variety of digital devices, from desktops to mobile phones. Anyone seeking employment                    that involves digital interactive media can gain an edge in the job market with the Rich                    Media Communication using Adobe® Flash® certification.                </p>            </div>        </div>    </div>    <div class = "panel panel-default">        <div class = "panel-heading">            <h4 class = "panel-title">                <a href = "#collapseFive" data-parent = "#accordion" data-toggle = "collapse" class = "accordion-toggle">                    EASY-TO-ADMINISTER EXAM REPLICATES REAL EXPERIENCE                </a>            </h4>        </div>        <div class = "panel-collapse collapse" id = "collapseFive">            <div class = "panel-body">                <p>                    Adobe Certified Associate exams incorporate both knowledge and performance-based                    questions that replicate real application experience by testing hands-on skills in Adobe®                    Flash.® The exam can be easily administered onsite or at a local testing center. To learn more                    about the tasks within the exam visit: www.adobe.com/ education/resources/ace/topics.html.                    The exam was created by leading educators and is designed to seamlessly complement your                    curriculum.                </p>             </div>        </div>    </div>    <div class = "panel panel-default">        <div class = "panel-heading">            <h4 class = "panel-title">                <a href = "#collapseSix" data-parent = "#accordion" data-toggle = "collapse" class = "accordion-toggle">                    PROVIDES INSTRUCTORS WITH POWERFUL IN-CLASS RESOURCES                </a>            </h4>        </div>        <div class = "panel-collapse collapse" id = "collapseSix">            <div class = "panel-body">                <p>                    Incorporate the exam into current courses to measure success                     <br /> Provide students with a highly marketable credential and expertise                     <br /> Answer the demand for certification in rich media communications                     <br /> Take advantage of today’s powerful digital testing and auto-scoring software                     <br /> Access free curriculum from Adobe® Education, which maps to the exam                    objectives at www.adobe.com/education/instruction/teach/digitalcareers                     <br /> Prove student’s hands-on skills with performance-based tests                </p>            </div>        </div>    </div>    <div class = "panel panel-default">        <div class = "panel-heading">            <h4 class = "panel-title">                <a href = "#collapseSeven" data-parent = "#accordion" data-toggle = "collapse" class = "accordion-toggle">                    HELPS STUDENTS LEARN MORE AND PROVE IT                </a>            </h4>        </div>        <div class = "panel-collapse collapse" id = "collapseSeven">            <div class = "panel-body">                <p>                    Certification validates their newly-acquired expertise in the Flash authoring tool                     <br /> Demonstrates a student’s core skills and knowledge using Adobe® applications                     <br /> Effectively tests the ability to develop rich interactive content for use in Web sites,                    online advertisements, instructional media, presentations, games, and more.                     <br /> Provides the foundation necessary to further enhance productivity and                    marketability with other digital media skills                </p>             </div>        </div>    </div></div>